Author: gimmethatdamnavocado
Text: Me too. I feel like there’s at least something that I can control in my life and it makes me feel good. But sadly I think it’s controlling more me than I am controlling it.

Author: Dalos_
Text: It’s such a sick disease. It makes us crave its safety and power and we’re left even more powerless and out of control against it. But does that stop us from glorifying it in our heads? Nope. I do it all the time. That’s why we need others around us to keep us reasonable. EDs only take away from you. And that’s the monk fruit sweetened tea. Fuck Ed but also... can’t wait to lose more weight. I feel this.
